OL,3,CCooper pledges crackdown on 'hateful
OL,4,Cbeliefs' to counter extremism
OL,6,FA review into extremism in the UK will
OL,7,Fdrive a counter strategy to respond to
OL,8,Fgrowing and changing patterns across
OL,9,Fthe nation, ITV News' David Wood has
OL,10,Fthe latest
OL,12,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper pledged
OL,13,Fto crack down on people "pushing
OL,14,Fharmful and hateful beliefs" and to
OL,15,F"kickstart" a new approach to fighting
OL,16,Fextremism.
OL,18,FThe Home Office has commissioned a
OL,19,F"rapid sprint" to drive a new
OL,20,Fpractical approach to countering
OL,21,Fextremism.
