OL,6,FThe project is being carried out to
OL,7,Fprovide analysis and recommendations
OL,8,Fon how to "tackle the threat posed by
OL,9,Fextremist ideologies".
OL,11,FIt will inform a new government
OL,12,Fcounter-extremism strategy to respond
OL,13,Fto growing and changing patterns
OL,14,Facross the UK.
