OL,4,Cbeliefs' to counter extremism
OL,6,FThe government said the scheme will
OL,7,Flook across the ideological spectrum,
OL,8,Fand address "gaps in the current
OL,9,Fsystem" which leave the country
OL,10,Fexposed to hateful activity that
OL,11,Fpromotes violence or undermines
OL,12,Fdemocracy.
OL,14,FAfter the riots that broke out across
OL,15,FEngland following the stabbing of
OL,16,Fthree girls in Southport, a total of
OL,17,F460 people had appeared in
OL,18,Fmagistrates' courts relating to the
OL,19,Fdisorder by the end of Thursday.
