OL,6,F"Hateful incitement of all kinds
OL,7,Ffractures and frays the very fabric of
OL,8,Four communities and our democracy.
OL,10,F"Action against extremism has been
OL,11,Fbadly hollowed out in recent years,
OL,12,Fjust when it should have been needed
OL,13,Fmost.
