OL,6,F"That's why I have directed the Home
OL,7,FOffice to conduct a rapid analytical
OL,8,Fsprint on extremism, to map and
OL,9,Fmonitor extremist trends, to
OL,10,Funderstand the evidence about what
OL,11,Fworks to disrupt and divert people
OL,12,Faway from extremist views, and to
OL,13,Fidentify any gaps in existing policy
OL,14,Fwhich need to be addressed to crack
OL,15,Fdown on those pushing harmful and
OL,16,Fhateful beliefs and violence.
